UNITED STATES of America v. Isom Edward ROSS, Administrator of the Estate of John H. Ross, Deceased, et al. No. 632. Circuit Court oil Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Feb. 23, 1932. Fred A. Wagoner, Asst. U. S. Atty., of Oklahoma City, Okl. J. H. Stolper, of Muskogee, Okl., for ap-pellees.
